title: Cerebellum

creator: Cerebellum Academy
descriptionHtml:
Cerebellum Academy is the Brainchild of Five top leading educators of India who are not only great academicians but extremely well read and gifted authors and motivators to millions of medical students. Respecting the meaning of its name, Cerebellum, a part of the brain responsible for balance, Cerebellum Academy will guide budding doctors across the nation to get their Balance of Knowledge and Skills right.

With the increasing competition in this fast-paced world, career related insecurities are a major reason for students feeling under-confident. Cerebellum Academy will train students and try to build their concepts and skills of medical and allied sciences, train them in the art and craft of solving questions and eventually try to create better clinicians. Working along the lines of this aim, the Core members of Cerebellum Academy have a team of equally capable educators under a single roof, teaching and motivating the students to “Get Their Balance Right”.

These top educationalists have combined taught over 10 lakhs students in their career and with their contagious energy they are addictive. With this institute and tailor-made courses for the students, they want the students to believe that they can not only clear INI CET, FMGE and NEET PG exams but also excel in the exam of life.

Our Aim:

For the first time in Indian history, 5 Leading educators along with all-time favourite teachers Dr. Zainab Vora and Dr. Dilip Kumar Ravi Kumar have come together on one single platform, Cerebellum Academy, to provide Conceptual, Clinical, Comprehensive, Relevant, and Revisable content to PG Aspirants to help them crack the most dreaded Medical PG Entrance Exams – NEET, INI CET & FMGE. Cerebellum Academy aims to provide top-notch teaching by the best educators of India with a combined teaching experience that crosses 100 plus years of wisdom and knowledge.

Online & Offline courses organised by Cerebellum academy are most sought after by students willing to get that extra cutting edge. The main agenda behind these courses is to give Relevant, Concise, Revisable content to students. In this competitive world there are no second chances and with even a few MCQ’s going wrong can end hopes of a dream seat. Hence, we strive to push you so hard that you will be used to mental challenges and will fire your neurons till the very moment when the buzzer of exam time is blown.

Our Vision:

Cerebellum academy, the best PG medical entrance exam academy is based on the vision to make medical entrance exam preparation simplified and easy so that students fall in love with the subjects instead of dreading them.

Our Mission:

Instilled with the aim to help students achieve their future, we have been working relentlessly to provide the best of educational services. Our efforts have helped us establish a formidable reputation for delivering qualitative and innovative teaching standards. We are dedicated to helping our students in making the best grades that will translate into a fulfilling career.
